---
title: Synthesis — Phase 3 (Blindspot Detection + Verdict Synthesis)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant ORC as Orchestrator
    participant OYDB as Orchestrator<br/>YottaDB
    participant BS as blindspot-detector<br/>(MCP Server)
    participant BS_YDB as blindspot-detector<br/>YottaDB
    participant CL_MCP as coverage-left<br/>(MCP Server)
    participant CC_MCP as coverage-center<br/>(MCP Server)
    participant CR_MCP as coverage-right<br/>(MCP Server)
    participant SYNTH as synthesizer<br/>(MCP Server)
    participant SYNTH_YDB as synthesizer<br/>YottaDB
    participant OMIRTH as Orchestrator<br/>Mirth

    Note over ORC,OMIRTH: Precondition: all 5 parallel agents complete.<br/>Phase 3a — Blindspot Detection (pull pattern)

    ORC->>BS: MCP invoke_task({run_id, task: "analyze_blindspot"})

    BS-->>ORC: MCP tool_request: get_observations(run_id, "COVERAGE_*")

    ORC->>CL_MCP: get_observations(run_id, "COVERAGE_*")
    CL_MCP-->>ORC: 4 OBX rows (article_count=12, framing=SUPPORTIVE, ...)

    ORC->>CC_MCP: get_observations(run_id, "COVERAGE_*")
    CC_MCP-->>ORC: 4 OBX rows (article_count=8, framing=CRITICAL, ...)

    ORC->>CR_MCP: get_observations(run_id, "COVERAGE_*")
    CR_MCP-->>ORC: 4 OBX rows (article_count=11, framing=CRITICAL, ...)

    ORC-->>BS: consolidated COVERAGE_* rows from all 3 agents

    BS->>BS: compute coverage asymmetry score<br/>left=12 SUPPORTIVE, center=8 CRITICAL,<br/>right=11 CRITICAL → no major blindspot

    BS->>BS_YDB: tool: add_observation(BLINDSPOT_SCORE, 0.12, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(BLINDSPOT_DIRECTION, NONE, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(CROSS_SPECTRUM_CORROBORATION, FALSE, F)

    BS->>OMIRTH: MLLP ACK
    ORC->>OYDB: blindspot-detector = COMPLETE

    Note over ORC,SYNTH_YDB: Phase 3b — Synthesis (pull pattern)<br/>All 10 agents now complete. Orchestrator<br/>assembles consolidated OBX log.

    ORC->>ORC: collect get_observations(run_id)<br/>from all 10 agent MCP servers

    ORC->>SYNTH: MCP invoke_task({<br/>  run_id,<br/>  consolidated_obx_log: [all F/C rows from all agents]<br/>})

    Note over SYNTH: Synthesizer applies DetermineOBXResolution<br/>DMN to resolve authoritative value per code.<br/>Computes weighted confidence score.

    SYNTH->>SYNTH: resolve authoritative OBX per code<br/>apply confidence weights:<br/>  claimreview_match: 0.35<br/>  domain_evidence: 0.30<br/>  cross_spectrum: 0.20<br/>  blindspot_penalty: -0.10<br/>  → CONFIDENCE_SCORE = 0.31

    SYNTH->>SYNTH: map 0.31 → MOSTLY_FALSE<br/>(range: 0.25–0.44)

    SYNTH->>SYNTH_YDB: tool: add_observation(CONFIDENCE_SCORE, 0.31, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(VERDICT, MOSTLY_FALSE, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(VERDICT_NARRATIVE, "...", F)<br/>tool: add_observation(SYNTHESIS_SIGNAL_COUNT, 28, F)<br/>tool: add_observation(SYNTHESIS_OVERRIDE_REASON, "", F)

    Note over SYNTH: Checks if VERDICT differs from CLAIMREVIEW_VERDICT.<br/>PolitiFact said MOSTLY_FALSE. System agrees.<br/>SYNTHESIS_OVERRIDE_REASON left empty.

    SYNTH->>OMIRTH: MLLP — send finalized HL7v2 message<br/>(all OBX rows from all agents + synthesis rows)

    OMIRTH-->>SYNTH: ACK AA

    ORC->>OYDB: synthesizer = COMPLETE<br/>^RUN(run_id, "status") = "SYNTHESIZED"<br/>^RUN(run_id, "terminal_obx_count") = 10

    Note over ORC,OMIRTH: SYNTHESIZED state triggers edge serialization.<br/>Orchestrator Mirth detects VERDICT F-status OBX<br/>and routes to edge adapter channel.
